			<p>Created by <a href="http://twitter.com/petetak">Pete Nelson</a>, <a href="http://twitter.com/neiltak">Neil Kinnish</a> &amp; <a href="http://twitter.com/domtak">Dom Murphy</a>.</p><p>Sparked to life from an initial desire to create quick &amp; focused screencasts. We decided it was the perfect project we could 'hack' together very quickly.</p><p>As it's been developed rapidly you will no doubt encounter the odd issue and of course the project can always be improved. If you would like to suggest improvements please <a href="http://twitter.com/quickcast">let us know on Twitter</a> or use the relevant issue tracker on GitHub &mdash; It's open source so please get involved.</p><p>If you have more questions, you may find the answers in our <a href="/faqs">FAQs</a>.</p>
